display.title: Iridium, Osmium, and EV
description: Yo, a quick note on &&aIridium&&r and &&aOsmium&&r.

We know, it's technically possible to obtain these materials now, but you should wait until you reach &&9IV&&r. Producing these materials will suck up a lot of your precious power... and you won't be able to smelt them into ingots until &&9IV&&r anyway!

subtitle.text: Hold your fire just for now
